data.title: filter rows
data.description: Filter for including only specific Rows for Webstore Data
data.code:
def filter_rows (data: pd.DataFrame) -> pd.DataFrame:
    data['order_date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['order_date'])
    current_month = datetime.now().month
    filtered_data = data[data['order_date'].dt.month == current_month]
    #only include completed
    return filtered_data[filtered_data['status'] == 'complete']
